# pythia CODEOWNERS — review routing for the public OSS repo.
#
# Each pattern is matched in order; later patterns override earlier ones
# for files that match both. The pattern owner is auto-requested on PRs
# that touch a matching file. If review is required by branch
# protection, an OWNER must approve before merge.
#
# Membership: maintainers belong to the @athanor-ai/pythia-maintainers
# team. Externally-contributed PRs default to that team. As the project
# scales, sub-teams below let domain experts review their lane.

# ─── Default catch-all ──────────────────────────────────────────────
*                                          @athanor-ai/pythia-maintainers

# ─── Library core (Lean) ────────────────────────────────────────────
/Pythia/                                   @athanor-ai/pythia-maintainers
/Pythia/Tactic/                            @athanor-ai/pythia-maintainers
/Pythia/AxiomAudit.lean                    @athanor-ai/pythia-maintainers
/Pythia.lean                               @athanor-ai/pythia-maintainers
/lakefile.lean                             @athanor-ai/pythia-maintainers
/lake-manifest.json                        @athanor-ai/pythia-maintainers
/lean-toolchain                            @athanor-ai/pythia-maintainers

